Comment: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,十分渺小也說不定
Comment: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是!
Comment: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這一步
Comment: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將是我們人類
