Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}集合!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來我將說明關於奪回托洛斯特區的作戰計畫!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}首先我來介紹這位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隸屬於訓練兵團的艾連．葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是我們秘密研究的巨人化活體實驗的成功案例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}變成巨人後的他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會抬起前門附近的那顆大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}搬到被破壞的門旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將洞口封住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們的任務則是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在他搬動岩石的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保護他免於受到其他巨人的攻擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}當這次作戰成功之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會是人類首次成功地把領土從巨人手中給搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這或許跟人類被搶走的東西相比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}十分渺小也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將是我們人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}偉大的進擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你不認識我了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}家人!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}閃開 阿卡曼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙是怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過是個腦袋不怎麼好的普通巨人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰計畫改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}直到回收葉卡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保護他免於遭受巨人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他對人類來說是一個珍貴的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是可以這麼簡單就捨去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是家裡啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼不使用立體機動裝置?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}故障了嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總會有辦法啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失敗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為不能丟下艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以大家都在奮戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再這麼下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人太多 可能會導致全軍覆沒!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從頭部後方到脖子...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}長一公尺!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}寬10公分!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明走出牆外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是個地獄般的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼艾連還是想去外面的世界呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你問我為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我 就是出生在這世界上的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我竟然在拖人後腿是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有什麼辦法了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}班長 到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只剩下我們而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}暫時先撤退到岩石那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}情況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}五個巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從大門過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可能在這裡等到巨人都消失為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然是立體機動裝置...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是的 別給我找麻煩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼扳機這麼硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你才是咧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點跳上來!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們根本在亂來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亂來的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有活下來的真實感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連他贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在他要去完成他自己的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下來只要掩護艾連到大門那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們就贏了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死守啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是拼上老命也要給我撐住!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保護艾連走到大門!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不要讓巨人接近!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別讓他們來妨礙 來去掩護艾連啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們兩個去艾連的身邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是命令!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米塔比班...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們在幹什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些巨人並沒有來吃我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以只能在被吃掉之前盡量往巨人接近!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快看這邊 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然我就把這根刺進你屁眼 幹掉你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}兩個上鉤了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跑到建築物那邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到地上簡直是自殺行為...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有馬和建築物根本無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在也只能這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}緊跟著米塔比班!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來這裡!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經快要撐不住了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走在那種地方的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會變成巨人的食物啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 快點過來啊 你這小嫩嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來這啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米塔比!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼艾連會想去外面的世界呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打從出生起...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是自由的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這跟拒絕接受「人生而自由」的人強勢與否...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根本毫無關係!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管是燃燒的水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或是冰凍的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都無所謂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}凡是看過它的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會是這世界上得到最大自由的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算要犧牲生命也在所不惜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}儘管這世界再怎麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也毫無關係!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算這世界再怎麼殘酷...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也沒有任何關係!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有巨人在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這邊讓我來!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我從那滾開!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上啊!!! 艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰鬥吧!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}犧牲有意義了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類在今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}第一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}戰勝巨人了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}確認到黃色信號彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰...應該是成功了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻派人前去支援!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把精銳班給救出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下的巨人靠過來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該爬上牆壁了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把艾連救出後我就會立刻離開!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他超乎想像的熱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}必須趕快爬上城牆才行...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}部分的身體已經結合在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拔也拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只好切掉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自由...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}之翼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在是什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在急忙趕來的調查軍團與駐紮軍團工兵部的表現下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆再次阻擋了巨人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}掃蕩被困在托洛斯特區內巨人的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就花了整整一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這期間 牆上固定砲的砲火不曾間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聚集在城牆邊的巨人幾乎都是被榴彈給打死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}倖存的巨人也被調查軍團給殲滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那時候成功活捉了4公尺級巨人跟7公尺級巨人各一名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死亡、失蹤者 共207名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}負傷者 897名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}儘管這是人類頭一次成功阻止了巨人的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相對於這份喜悅  失去的人數實在是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你知道他的名字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想說一直沒看到...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只有他...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可能的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底發生了什麼事...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有...有誰...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有誰看到他是怎麼死的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}知道的話就快點回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你知道嗎? 訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用岩石封住洞口已經過了兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是我們還沒完成屍體的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再拖下去可能會爆發傳染病的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們必須遏止二次災害的發生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在沒時間去感嘆同伴陣亡這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你能理解嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}第104期...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隸屬於訓練兵團...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}19班班長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可．波特...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幸好你知道他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繼續作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是巨人吐出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為他們沒消化器官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吃了人之後 一旦飽了就會像這樣子吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他媽的... 這樣子根本就分不出誰是誰了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}道歉也沒辦法改變什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們還是趕緊替他們收屍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有什麼想問的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團實行部隊的領導者...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文團長以及...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如你所見 這裡是地牢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在的你在憲兵團的管轄之下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才我們好不容易才獲准和你接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那把鑰匙...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊... 這是你戴在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}晚點會還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的老家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在希干希納區葉卡醫生家的地下室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那裡藏有著巨人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的... 應該沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我父親他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你喪失記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而父親又失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也未免太巧合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該已經得出結論說他沒有任何理由要去說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然還有很多事情尚待釐清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過現在該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是聽聽你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的想法是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了調查你的老家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們必須搶回希干希納區的瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要以最快的速度將遭到破壞的那扇門給封起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最好的方法...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你那身「巨人之力」是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然最後左右我們命運的還是巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「超大型巨人」跟「盔甲巨人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想必原理應該是與你相同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的想法將會是「關鍵」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將人類從絕望之中拯救出來的「關鍵」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺光你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上一隻不留地...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 快點回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想做的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}加入調查軍團...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之就是想痛宰那些巨人
